00:01:44.380 --> 00:01:46.300
(Yunlai Tavern)

00:01:50.320 --> 00:01:51.780
Taverns used to open on the 10th day,

00:01:52.320 --> 00:01:53.800
but Shen's Diner opened on the 6th,

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:56.190
even imitating the imperial dishes

00:01:56.190 --> 00:01:57.070
like

00:01:57.550 --> 00:01:58.550
Little Spring Platter.

00:01:59.630 --> 00:02:01.430
Warm spring water

00:02:01.880 --> 00:02:03.600
is rare at this time of year.

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:05.240
At the beginning of spring,

00:02:05.630 --> 00:02:07.160
only the homes of nobles

00:02:07.160 --> 00:02:08.430
can draw on hot spring water

00:02:08.430 --> 00:02:09.870
to grow some fruits and vegetables.

00:02:10.400 --> 00:02:11.590
They can let their guests

00:02:11.590 --> 00:02:13.360
enjoy melons and vegetables now.

00:02:13.590 --> 00:02:15.200
That's quite an accomplishment.

00:02:15.680 --> 00:02:17.750
But they're not using hot spring water.

00:02:18.150 --> 00:02:19.150
They've leased the land

00:02:19.150 --> 00:02:21.240
and used oil paper and bamboo to create

00:02:21.240 --> 00:02:22.830
a temperature-controlled frame.

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:25.270
They call it

00:02:25.960 --> 00:02:27.200
greenhouse cultivation.

00:02:27.920 --> 00:02:28.970
They even taught this trick

00:02:28.970 --> 00:02:30.340
to the farmers around the Capital

00:02:30.430 --> 00:02:31.430
and fooled them

00:02:31.430 --> 00:02:32.990
into waiving rent

00:02:33.550 --> 00:02:35.240
and supplying them with vegetables.

00:02:39.480 --> 00:02:41.200
Today, we're here to congratulate them.

00:02:41.830 --> 00:02:43.550
Why are you being so petty?

00:02:44.310 --> 00:02:45.200
Sorry.

00:02:47.870 --> 00:02:49.080
Why so nervous?

00:02:51.270 --> 00:02:53.080
This place is bustling with people.

00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:54.200
If you make people think

00:02:54.200 --> 00:02:56.150
that I usually mistreat my servants,

00:02:56.590 --> 00:02:57.750
I'll have you killed.

00:02:57.750 --> 00:02:58.680
I understand.

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:00.040
I understand.

00:03:02.820 --> 00:03:05.960
(Shen's Diner)

00:03:05.990 --> 00:03:07.200
- Welcome.
- Lady Shen.

00:03:10.870 --> 00:03:12.200
On behalf of Yunlai Tavern,

00:03:12.520 --> 00:03:13.830
I'm here to congratulate you

00:03:13.830 --> 00:03:15.920
on the Chinese New Year
and the renovation.

00:03:16.640 --> 00:03:19.080
(This is the arch-rival from Yunlai.)

00:03:20.150 --> 00:03:22.590
(A typical villainous,
refined male antagonist.)

00:03:24.710 --> 00:03:26.800
So, you are the owner of Yunlai Tavern,

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:28.030
Mr. Lu Yun.

00:03:28.240 --> 00:03:29.080
How thoughtful.

00:03:29.080 --> 00:03:30.310
Please come in and have a seat.

00:03:30.640 --> 00:03:31.680
You must be busy.

00:03:31.680 --> 00:03:32.550
When you have time,

00:03:32.550 --> 00:03:33.830
I'll come again for a cup of tea.

00:03:46.240 --> 00:03:48.120
Only you will have time for this.

00:03:52.920 --> 00:03:54.240
Every time I see it, I'm repulsed.

00:03:54.330 --> 00:03:55.710
What's wrong with the people here?

00:03:55.710 --> 00:03:56.650
Everything new

00:03:56.660 --> 00:03:57.980
ends up warding off evil.

00:04:00.430 --> 00:04:01.400
Welcome.

00:04:02.870 --> 00:04:04.350
You can eat at Yunlai Tavern anytime,

00:04:04.350 --> 00:04:05.990
but if we miss
the Little Spring Platter,

00:04:05.990 --> 00:04:07.170
it won't be available anymore.

00:04:07.170 --> 00:04:08.010
Let's go.

00:04:09.990 --> 00:04:10.830
How about

00:04:11.150 --> 00:04:12.920
you ask Noble Consort Dou

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:14.620
to find a way to deal with them?

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:16.680
Lin Yan rose to power

00:04:16.680 --> 00:04:18.280
after dealing with her relatives.

00:04:18.480 --> 00:04:20.040
He's backing Shen's Diner.

00:04:22.680 --> 00:04:24.440
Yet, he's won the favor
of Chancellor Meng

00:04:24.440 --> 00:04:25.830
thanks to the Appeal drum.

00:04:26.120 --> 00:04:26.960
Chancellor Meng

00:04:27.430 --> 00:04:30.040
is planning to marry
his granddaughter to him.

00:04:32.120 --> 00:04:34.480
Lin Yan will eventually distance himself
from his cousin.

00:04:36.340 --> 00:04:40.980
(Shi'an County)

00:04:41.510 --> 00:04:42.390
Young Master,

00:04:42.390 --> 00:04:43.230
this is the place.

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:48.560
Young Master.

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:52.190
Sorry,

00:04:52.190 --> 00:04:53.070
sir.

00:04:53.480 --> 00:04:54.320
It's alright.

00:04:58.160 --> 00:04:59.600
Lady Zheng, you're pregnant.

00:04:59.800 --> 00:05:00.750
Please be careful.

00:05:01.310 --> 00:05:03.070
How did you know I'm a Zheng?

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:06.190
I am Liu Chang,

00:05:06.190 --> 00:05:07.510
a deputy in the Prefecture,

00:05:07.510 --> 00:05:09.360
sent to investigate
the Magistrate of Shi'an.

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:11.480
I'm Cheng Hu, a deputy

00:05:12.280 --> 00:05:13.120
in the Prefecture.

00:05:13.620 --> 00:05:14.840
You're here for the Magistrate?

00:05:14.840 --> 00:05:16.240
I have so much to say.

00:05:16.920 --> 00:05:18.360
The magistrate is truly kind.

00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:19.200
Come in for some tea.

00:05:19.840 --> 00:05:20.680
Thank you.

00:05:22.920 --> 00:05:23.760
Please.

00:05:27.600 --> 00:05:28.550
Please sit here first.

00:05:28.550 --> 00:05:29.720
I'll go prepare the tea.

00:05:31.310 --> 00:05:32.990
The tea here is wonderful,

00:05:33.280 --> 00:05:35.280
fragrant and rich,

00:05:35.280 --> 00:05:36.390
refreshing

00:05:36.390 --> 00:05:37.360
to the heart and soul,

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:38.200
sweet and lingering.

00:05:39.070 --> 00:05:39.910
Have your seat.

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:47.430
She's so talkative.

00:05:47.750 --> 00:05:49.360
I didn't expect it.

00:05:49.800 --> 00:05:50.840
When I came before,

00:05:50.840 --> 00:05:52.750
I just asked around the neighborhood,

00:05:52.750 --> 00:05:54.390
but I didn't see her in person.

00:05:56.620 --> 00:05:58.320
If you want to know
about the Magistrate,

00:05:58.320 --> 00:05:59.240
ask me.

00:05:59.240 --> 00:06:00.080
The Magistrate

00:06:00.180 --> 00:06:02.040
is a truly good man.

00:06:02.390 --> 00:06:04.280
One of a kind in the world.

00:06:04.430 --> 00:06:06.390
He's handsome, gentle,
considerate, and upright.

00:06:06.990 --> 00:06:07.950
His only hobby is

00:06:07.950 --> 00:06:09.050
advocating for the people.

00:06:11.310 --> 00:06:12.150
Thank you.

00:06:13.190 --> 00:06:14.680
No need to trouble yourself.

00:06:25.480 --> 00:06:26.870
These are not for us?

00:06:30.190 --> 00:06:31.030
Sorry.

00:06:31.190 --> 00:06:32.240
I'm pregnant

00:06:32.240 --> 00:06:33.180
and get hungry easily.

00:06:33.720 --> 00:06:34.560
Help yourselves.

00:06:38.160 --> 00:06:39.280
Thank you.

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:42.280
Not for me.

00:06:42.280 --> 00:06:43.950
Try some. A local specialty.

00:06:51.950 --> 00:06:52.790
How is it?

00:06:52.950 --> 00:06:54.190
Is this water shield pastry?

00:06:55.040 --> 00:06:57.360
The water shield in Shi'an
and Qingyang grows very well.

00:06:57.390 --> 00:06:58.240
Not long ago,

00:06:58.240 --> 00:06:59.390
someone even came all the way

00:06:59.400 --> 00:07:01.170
from Yong'an to pick some.

00:07:01.550 --> 00:07:02.840
These water shields

00:07:03.040 --> 00:07:05.040
were given by Lady Shen,

00:07:05.040 --> 00:07:06.680
who came to pick water shields.

00:07:07.160 --> 00:07:09.510
She was covered in injuries that day.

00:07:09.750 --> 00:07:11.310
I thought something had happened,

00:07:11.510 --> 00:07:14.800
but it turned out she got hurt
picking these water shields.

00:07:15.160 --> 00:07:17.190
She must've craved this

00:07:17.390 --> 00:07:18.480
so much

00:07:18.480 --> 00:07:19.600
as to go to such lengths.

00:07:51.510 --> 00:07:52.870
Do you also like this?

00:07:53.120 --> 00:07:55.280
I thought only people
from Qingyang loved it.

00:07:56.430 --> 00:07:57.280
People from Qingyang?

00:08:02.160 --> 00:08:03.840
Are you perhaps

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:04.680
from Qingyang?

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:09.280
When I was a child,

00:08:10.120 --> 00:08:11.430
I was engaged in Qingyang,

00:08:12.040 --> 00:08:13.750
but that family got into trouble,

00:08:14.280 --> 00:08:15.430
and the whole clan perished.

00:08:16.920 --> 00:08:18.160
Fearing entanglement,

00:08:18.160 --> 00:08:19.190
my family moved to Shi'an

00:08:19.680 --> 00:08:20.870
and never dared to go back.

00:08:21.720 --> 00:08:22.560
Unexpectedly,

00:08:23.070 --> 00:08:24.310
last September,

00:08:24.680 --> 00:08:26.600
someone went to my relatives in Qingyang

00:08:26.600 --> 00:08:27.920
to ask about that engagement.

00:08:28.920 --> 00:08:29.990
I'm only telling you this

00:08:29.990 --> 00:08:31.800
because you are from the Prefecture.

00:08:31.990 --> 00:08:34.270
If that family back then
had a grievance,

00:08:34.270 --> 00:08:35.960
could you two perhaps help?

00:08:39.480 --> 00:08:41.150
We'd certainly not stand idly by.

00:08:41.750 --> 00:08:43.120
But please tell us

00:08:43.670 --> 00:08:44.870
what was

00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:46.320
asked about

00:08:46.750 --> 00:08:47.600
last September.

00:08:48.320 --> 00:08:49.160
It was...

00:08:53.720 --> 00:08:54.670
I don't want to say.

00:08:57.150 --> 00:08:58.720
- Well.
- The officialdom is complex.

00:08:59.080 --> 00:09:00.840
I don't know which side you are on.

00:09:00.840 --> 00:09:02.190
How could I just say these things?

00:09:10.790 --> 00:09:11.630
Well.

00:09:12.510 --> 00:09:13.350
In that case,

00:09:14.030 --> 00:09:16.200
thank you for the pastries and tea.

00:09:16.960 --> 00:09:17.800
Goodbye.

00:09:18.150 --> 00:09:18.990
Young Master.

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:20.200
Wait.

00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:24.630
I said all that just now

00:09:24.990 --> 00:09:26.390
to make you two anxious.

00:09:27.270 --> 00:09:28.600
When people get anxious,

00:09:29.030 --> 00:09:30.960
they reveal their true character.

00:09:31.630 --> 00:09:33.390
If you had threatened me just now,

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:34.960
then I wouldn't say

00:09:34.960 --> 00:09:35.990
anything at all.

00:09:37.630 --> 00:09:38.960
You're all alone.

00:09:39.630 --> 00:09:40.720
How bold of you.

00:09:41.150 --> 00:09:42.270
The Magistrate here

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:43.630
is my husband.

00:09:44.630 --> 00:09:45.670
In Shi'an County,

00:09:46.080 --> 00:09:47.390
I don't have much to fear.

00:09:47.630 --> 00:09:48.560
The Magistrate?

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:51.720
But your house...

00:09:52.790 --> 00:09:54.390
It's a bit modest.

00:09:54.670 --> 00:09:57.440
My husband only wants
to serve the people.

00:09:57.600 --> 00:09:59.200
He's earned a good reputation.

00:10:00.200 --> 00:10:02.670
You claimed to be here
for the Magistrate,

00:10:02.670 --> 00:10:04.240
yet you didn't know my identity.

00:10:05.030 --> 00:10:06.840
What you want to know

00:10:07.140 --> 00:10:08.440
must be the old case, right?

00:10:09.030 --> 00:10:09.870
Exactly.

00:10:13.720 --> 00:10:14.630
I am Lin Yan,

00:10:15.030 --> 00:10:16.420
Vice Prefecture of the Prefecture,

00:10:16.670 --> 00:10:18.720
investigating the Qingyang Cui case.

00:10:31.480 --> 00:10:32.990
My husband and I both believe

00:10:33.560 --> 00:10:35.080
that the Prefect

00:10:35.080 --> 00:10:36.270
could never have done that.

00:10:36.990 --> 00:10:37.840
In the ninth month,

00:10:38.240 --> 00:10:40.560
a man approached my great-uncle,

00:10:40.990 --> 00:10:43.440
inquiring about the Cui
and Zheng marriage.

00:10:43.990 --> 00:10:45.270
My great-uncle was wary

00:10:45.630 --> 00:10:47.480
and saw through his false name,

00:10:47.480 --> 00:10:48.720
so he brushed him off.

00:10:49.360 --> 00:10:52.080
I asked my husband
to find out who that man is,

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:53.160
and he turned out

00:10:53.560 --> 00:10:56.270
to be the fourth son of Prince Zhao,

00:10:56.560 --> 00:10:57.400
Li Ang.

00:10:58.080 --> 00:10:59.240
If I remember correctly,

00:10:59.390 --> 00:11:01.320
you handled

00:11:01.510 --> 00:11:03.440
Magistrate Dou's embezzlement case.

00:11:03.720 --> 00:11:04.560
Yes.

00:11:04.790 --> 00:11:05.670
Actually, my husband

00:11:05.840 --> 00:11:07.720
has been keeping an eye
on this case as well.

00:11:08.080 --> 00:11:10.390
Magistrate Dou is related
to Noble Consort Dou,

00:11:10.670 --> 00:11:11.910
and the money he embezzled

00:11:11.910 --> 00:11:13.390
all flowed back to the Dou family.

00:11:13.670 --> 00:11:16.190
Prince Zhao appears to be on bad terms
with Noble Consort Dou,

00:11:16.270 --> 00:11:17.200
but in private,

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:18.910
he's been in contact
with the Dou family.

00:11:19.440 --> 00:11:21.870
He's been dealing with the Capital,

00:11:22.030 --> 00:11:23.990
and he's concerned with the Cui case.

00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:25.870
So, these two cases might be

00:11:26.440 --> 00:11:27.990
the same one.

00:11:28.720 --> 00:11:29.670
Mr. Lin,

00:11:29.670 --> 00:11:31.030
Uncle Cui was too upright

00:11:31.030 --> 00:11:32.200
to sell official positions.

00:11:33.030 --> 00:11:34.030
Please investigate

00:11:34.030 --> 00:11:34.870
this old case.

00:11:41.500 --> 00:11:44.620
(Shen's Diner)

00:11:49.870 --> 00:11:50.710
Young Master,

00:11:51.270 --> 00:11:53.320
we're passing by Shen's Diner.

00:11:53.670 --> 00:11:54.510
Shall we

00:11:54.870 --> 00:11:56.320
go in?

00:11:57.600 --> 00:11:58.440
No.

00:11:58.990 --> 00:11:59.910
Go to the Prefecture.

00:12:11.910 --> 00:12:13.240
Your Carefree Drink.

00:12:13.240 --> 00:12:14.150
Enjoy.

00:12:16.510 --> 00:12:17.360
Mr. Lin.

00:12:19.240 --> 00:12:20.080
- Wait.
- Father.

00:12:20.480 --> 00:12:21.790
- Uncle.
- Wait.

00:12:24.270 --> 00:12:25.110
Wait.

00:12:27.790 --> 00:12:28.630
Mr. Lin,

00:12:29.120 --> 00:12:30.510
we've just launched

00:12:30.510 --> 00:12:31.960
the Little Spring Platter.

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:33.990
I was thinking of sending some over,

00:12:34.320 --> 00:12:35.440
and here you are.

00:12:35.440 --> 00:12:36.280
What a coincidence.

00:12:36.310 --> 00:12:37.200
Why don't you take some

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:38.240
to try at home?

00:12:39.630 --> 00:12:41.670
Deyuan, a Little Spring Platter.

00:12:41.670 --> 00:12:42.560
- Hurry up.
- Coming.

00:12:42.560 --> 00:12:43.910
Mr. Lin is here.

00:12:47.080 --> 00:12:47.920
No need.

00:12:51.870 --> 00:12:52.710
Liu Chang.

00:12:56.600 --> 00:12:57.560
Stop, stop.

00:12:57.560 --> 00:12:58.990
Sorry, please stop.

00:13:00.750 --> 00:13:01.590
Mr. Lin,

00:13:02.200 --> 00:13:04.670
when we make something delicious,

00:13:04.670 --> 00:13:06.420
we always want to share it
with our family.

00:13:06.960 --> 00:13:07.870
Why don't you

00:13:07.870 --> 00:13:08.870
give it a try?

00:13:09.600 --> 00:13:10.870
Yes, give it a try.

00:13:12.030 --> 00:13:13.030
Coming.

00:13:22.870 --> 00:13:23.710
Well.

00:13:23.910 --> 00:13:25.560
Milady, it's ready.

00:13:48.960 --> 00:13:50.560
Please, accept it.

