♪This mundane heart, unwilling to fade♪

00:13:54.520 --> 00:13:57.920
♪Perhaps foreknew heaven's design♪

00:13:57.920 --> 00:14:01.000
♪Thus fled destiny's trace♪

00:14:01.360 --> 00:14:04.240
♪Migrating toward you♪

00:14:05.680 --> 00:14:08.160
♪But worldly customs permit only♪

00:14:08.160 --> 00:14:11.640
♪Our fleeting meetings♪

00:14:11.680 --> 00:14:15.400
♪Granting us floods
